	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />One thing you could do is implement routines to draw the nametables. Just drawing the nametables is enough for simple but important games like Donkey Kong and DK Jr to run. Just take it a step at a time and don't attempt to do everything at once and do it all perfectly. The first time won't be perfect.

		

